684
00:50:08,000 --> 00:50:08,820
 neurološku,

685
00:50:08,820 --> 00:50:09,180
 recimo,

686
00:50:09,180 --> 00:50:09,880
 ako se javlju

687
00:50:09,880 --> 00:50:11,300
 epileptički napad

688
00:50:11,300 --> 00:50:12,760
