690
00:50:14,160 --> 00:50:14,920
 izbehandliti

691
00:50:14,920 --> 00:50:16,680
 u kućnim uvjetima ponekad

692
00:50:16,680 --> 00:50:17,640
 ili neke druge

693
00:50:17,640 --> 00:50:19,080
