694
00:50:19,080 --> 00:50:20,280
 onda imamo psihologa,

695
00:50:20,280 --> 00:50:21,780
 onda imamo psihijatra

696
00:50:21,780 --> 00:50:22,900
 koji kada vidimo

697
00:50:22,900 --> 00:50:23,860
 da je patologija

698
00:50:23,860 --> 00:50:24,960
 tako žestoka,

699
00:50:24,960 --> 00:50:27,980
 onda naš kolega Peharda

700
00:50:27,980 --> 00:50:28,340
 ide

701
00:50:28,340 --> 00:50:29,540
 ovaj

702
00:50:29,540 --> 00:50:30,980
 u kućnu posjetu,

703
00:50:30,980 --> 00:50:32,380
 tako da

704
00:50:32,380 --> 00:50:33,500
 imamo

705
00:50:33,500 --> 00:50:34,640
 istomatologa,

706
00:50:34,640 --> 00:50:35,020
 recimo,

707
00:50:35,020 --> 00:50:37,000
 imate jako zanimljivu situaciju,

708
00:50:37,000 --> 00:50:39,180
 čovjeku treba izvaditi zub,

709
00:50:39,180 --> 00:50:41,960
 on je teško pokristne,

710
00:50:41,960 --> 00:50:43,160
 ima jake bolove

711
00:50:43,160 --> 00:50:44,960
 i ne možeš ga nigdje izvaditi

712
00:50:44,960 --> 00:50:45,780
 nego u ambulantu

713
00:50:45,780 --> 00:50:46,680
 stomatološku,

714
00:50:46,680 --> 00:50:46,940
 dakle,

715
00:50:46,940 --> 00:50:48,140
 mi imamo stomatologa

716
00:50:48,140 --> 00:50:48,560
 koji to

717
00:50:48,560 --> 00:50:49,940
 radi doma,

718
00:50:49,940 --> 00:50:51,220
 radi ova naš doktor

719
00:50:51,220 --> 00:50:52,180
 Povar Zanović,

720
00:50:52,180 --> 00:50:53,280
 jasno ne,

721
00:50:53,280 --> 00:50:53,920
 da su tu

722
00:50:53,920 --> 00:50:55,620
 kolega Bilić

723
00:50:55,620 --> 00:50:56,400
 i kolega

724
00:50:56,400 --> 00:50:57,660
 Božec,

725
00:50:57,660 --> 00:50:59,820
 oni sa našim

726
00:50:59,820 --> 00:51:00,760
 sestramom

727
00:51:00,760 --> 00:51:02,420
 nije nužno

728
00:51:02,420 --> 00:51:03,140
 da svaki put

729
00:51:03,140 --> 00:51:04,260
 idu lječnik,

730
00:51:04,260 --> 00:51:04,560
 dakle,

731
00:51:04,560 --> 00:51:05,760
 nekad idu u tandemu

732
00:51:05,760 --> 00:51:07,540
 lječnik sestra,

733
00:51:07,540 --> 00:51:10,520
 a nekad ide lječnik

734
00:51:10,520 --> 00:51:11,600
 pa onda sestra,

735
00:51:11,600 --> 00:51:12,580
 nekad ide sestra

736
00:51:12,580 --> 00:51:13,220
 pa lječnik,

737
00:51:13,220 --> 00:51:13,460
 dakle,

738
00:51:13,460 --> 00:51:14,140
 sve zavisi

739
00:51:14,140 --> 00:51:15,420
 o tim procjenama,

740
00:51:15,420 --> 00:51:16,160
 onda oni imaju

741
00:51:16,160 --> 00:51:17,060
 svoje sastanke

742
00:51:17,060 --> 00:51:18,680
 i procjenjuju

743
00:51:18,680 --> 00:51:19,600
 što će dalje

744
00:51:19,600 --> 00:51:21,420
 tom bolesniku trebati.

745
00:51:21,420 --> 00:51:22,680
 Imamo

746
00:51:22,680 --> 00:51:23,460
 Županijski

747
00:51:23,460 --> 00:51:24,140
 taj projekt

748
