 ovaj

750
00:51:25,300 --> 00:51:26,320
 socijalna skrb

751
00:51:26,320 --> 00:51:27,320
 facilitira

752
00:51:27,320 --> 00:51:28,020
 nulazak

753
00:51:28,020 --> 00:51:28,740
 socijalnog

